  "instructions": [
    "In a small bowl, combine almond milk, yeast, and 1 tablespoon of honey. Let it sit for 5-7 minutes, or until the yeast becomes frothy.",
    "Preheat a toaster or toaster oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Toast the bread slices until they're lightly browned, about 2-3 minutes per side.",
    "In a blender or food processor, combine the remaining 1 tablespoon of honey, coconut oil, salt, basil leaves, almond butter, and Thai red chili flakes. Blend until smooth.",
    "Brush the toasted bread slices with the blended mixture. Top with a dollop of almond butter and a sprinkle of salt.",
    "Drizzle the yeasty almond milk mixture over the toast and garnish with a sprinkle of basil leaves.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
